{"tid":1295400,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[經典遊戲] 無差別警隊  回歸上線！","createTime":"2019-07-08T04:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T06:19:58.000Z","uid":38203,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8d8c5c7d92670aea4e7a57ede9831a4ff63197","tid":1295400,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YzXuw6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYzXuw6F.png&h=329bac29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0zhY9Tk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0zhY9Tk.png&h=182a1ee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有無認撚住依段童年回憶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：上網見到share，我無野講  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714e55595ce47070272fc5adf437a058e6e6b53e","tid":1295400,"uid":38203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:16:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1294335/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1294335/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2b65048da7b7b8531f7f0e84d1e404c5528f7d80","tid":1295400,"uid":38203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"714e55595ce47070272fc5adf437a058e6e6b53e","tid":1295400,"uid":38203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:16:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1294335/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1294335/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"[圖文\b] 7.7 克警資料整合<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1294335\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1294335</a>"},{"pid":"8cbbb73fb7ebd29d0ffa1914c32e2c8f61462198","tid":1295400,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"GAMEPLAY :<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>雖然啱先見到有差唔多post<br />\n但方便持續update所以開多過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位巴打請繼續更新 有link比link 有圖比圖<br />\n追究佢班仆街到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無法無天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>推撞記者</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tang.earthquake/videos/357223841635134/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftang.earthquake%2Fvideos%2F357223841635134%2F&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=60c56b52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tang.earthquake/videos/357223841635134/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fAqBfbaf_VE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfAqBfbaf_VE&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=bc4759bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fAqBfbaf_VE</a> (back up)<br />\n23623 朱運基 高級警員<br />\n16676 馮錦輝 警長<br />\n16990 <br />\n19450 <br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/66076417_2618548944823033_2239045977019252736_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQn3HbNa0CPgLe4rNvnhhrNS4S8MotLtZOVUNCegHtsCMjI32uimZcVs3QkL38w-TaE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=83fae63f85ccf1f43d6937d280eaa4b9&amp;oe=5DC2BB07\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F66076417_2618548944823033_2239045977019252736_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_oc%3DAQn3HbNa0CPgLe4rNvnhhrNS4S8MotLtZOVUNCegHtsCMjI32uimZcVs3QkL38w-TaE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D83fae63f85ccf1f43d6937d280eaa4b9%26oe%3D5DC2BB07&h=4dd94d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n21304  鍾俊邦 (名要fact check)